t = int(input())
for _ in range(t):
    n = int(input())
    m, p = list(map(int, input().split()))
    voters = [list(map(int, input().split())) for i in range(n)]

    cnt = 0
    for i in range(n-1, -1, -1):

            cnt += p

            cnt += min(p, voters[i] - voters[i+1])
    print(cnt)
